boiling-down price
Homonym Number:
Word Class: noun
Sense Number:  1
Definition:[stock sales] a low price such as that for surplus sheep boiled for tallow.


Origin: [none]
Register:
Register 2:
Flag: Farm Words
Domain: Rural
Region: [none]
